OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779203471
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer ruling out a timetable
OL,4,Cto quit is Olympic level straw-
OL,5,Cclutching
OL,7,FKeir Starmer does not want the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election to be an
OL,9,Fexplicit referendum on whether he
OL,10,Fshould remain prime minister.
OL,12,FWhich is why he has - just now - ruled
OL,13,Fout setting a timetable for his own
OL,14,Fresignation if Andy Burnham wins that
OL,15,Fby-election.
OL,17,FTruthfully this is Olympic level straw-
OL,18,Fclutching. It will be just such a
OL,19,Freferendum, whatever the PM says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
