OL,3,CPeston: Starmer ruling out a timetable
OL,4,Cto quit is Olympic level straw-
OL,5,Cclutching
OL,7,FI am not exaggerating.
OL,9,FTheir party is so ideologically riven
OL,10,Fand so weakened by factionalism that
OL,11,Fan emotional leadership contest that
OL,12,Fbarks like civil war may put paid to
OL,13,Fany rolling back of the stone and any
OL,14,Fescape from the grave.
